trans-unit.source: Specifies whether smoothing (antialiasing) is applied to lines and curves and the edges of filled areas.
trans-unit.target: Angir om utjevning (Anti-Aliasing) brukes til linjer og kurver og kantene for fylte områder.

trans-unit.source: Default, None, and HighSpeed are equivalent and specify rendering without smoothing applied.
trans-unit.target: Standard, og høy hastighet er like, og angi gjengivelse uten utjevning brukes.

trans-unit.source: AntiAlias and HighQuality are equivalent and specify rendering with smoothing applied.
trans-unit.target: AntiAlias og HighQuality er like, og angi gjengivelse med utjevning brukes.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > When the <xref:System.Drawing.Graphics.SmoothingMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property is specified by using the SmoothingMode enumeration, it does not affect text.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Når den <xref:System.Drawing.Graphics.SmoothingMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen er angitt ved hjelp av SmoothingMode opplistingen, påvirker ikke tekst.</xref:System.Drawing.Graphics.SmoothingMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: To set the text rendering quality, use the <xref:System.Drawing.Graphics.TextRenderingHint%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property and the <xref:System.Drawing.Text.TextRenderingHint> enumeration.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil angi teksten gjengivelse kvalitet, kan du bruke den <xref:System.Drawing.Graphics.TextRenderingHint%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen og <xref:System.Drawing.Text.TextRenderingHint>opplisting.</xref:System.Drawing.Text.TextRenderingHint> </xref:System.Drawing.Graphics.TextRenderingHint%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > When the<xref:System.Drawing.Graphics.SmoothingMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property is specified by using the SmoothingMode enumeration, it does not affect areas filled by a path gradient brush.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Når den<xref:System.Drawing.Graphics.SmoothingMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> egenskapen er angitt ved hjelp av SmoothingMode opplistingen, påvirker ikke områder som er fylt ut av en bane gradering velgeren.</xref:System.Drawing.Graphics.SmoothingMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Areas filled by using a <xref:System.Drawing.Drawing2D.PathGradientBrush> object are rendered the same way (aliased) regardless of the setting for the <xref:System.Drawing.Graphics.SmoothingMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: Områder fylt ved hjelp av en <xref:System.Drawing.Drawing2D.PathGradientBrush>objekt gjengis på samme måte (Alias) uavhengig av innstillingen for den <xref:System.Drawing.Graphics.SmoothingMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen.</xref:System.Drawing.Graphics.SmoothingMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Drawing.Drawing2D.PathGradientBrush>
